import React from 'react'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'
const Nav = () => {
    return (
        <nav class="list-group">
            <Link class="list-group-item active" to={"/profilemain"}> Account overview  </Link>
            <Link class="list-group-item" to={"/profileaddress"}> My Address </Link>
            <Link class="list-group-item" to={"/order"}> My Orders </Link>
            <Link class="list-group-item" to={"/wishlist"}> My wishlist </Link>
            <Link class="list-group-item" to={"/seller"}> My Selling Items </Link>
            <Link class="list-group-item" to={"/setting"}> Settings </Link>
            <Link class="list-group-item" to={"/login"}> Log out </Link>
        </nav>
    )
}

export default Nav
